{
  "stem": "7683.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I was not assigned to that because, as I say, officially I didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "October the 14th, 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew that is the day when it happened, so we went normally to work like always.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And ?] the only thing is through the time, we put away valuables.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The place where they burned the refuse-- papers, things like that-- I had the friend-- he was a friend of mine what [? was ?] [? a ?] working.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I always gave him valuables, and I put them-- took them and put them in the ground.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When it is a day, we go to run away, I go to take it with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the same day, already took-- The day before, I took all these things that was valuables, and I bandaged it on my leg because I couldn't keep it on me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I bandaged [? with ?] bandages on my leg, and that is the way I took with me valuables.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also, we took from the clothes what we were sorting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took some better clothes, because we wore-- we wore regular clothes, we didn't-- You did not wear uniforms?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have any camp stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had regular clothes, so we could, if a jacket was a good jacket, you took a jacket or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we took maybe two jackets with two pants or whatever because we knew today is the day we run away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while we're working, there was already going on-- there was the places where the tailor worked, the goldsmith, all these people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They worked for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made for them clothes, shoes, things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
